				Management effectiveness shows return on equity and return on assets for the trailing twelve months at -1.2% and -0.33% respectively. During the same quarter previous year, the firm posted ($0.53) earnings per share.While looking at the Stock's Performance, Abercrombie & Fitch Co. now shows a Weekly Performance of 7.31%, where Monthly Performance is -24.23%, Quarterly performance is -14.13%, 6 Months performance is -21.03% and yearly performance percentage is -51.67%.Abercrombie & Fitch Company (NYSE:ANF) last announced its quarterly earnings data on Thursday, May 25th. If you are reading this piece on another site, it was stolen and reposted in violation of worldwide copyright legislation. The correct version of this piece can be viewed at https://www.baseball-news-blog.com/2017/07/22/abercrombie-fitch-company-nyseanf-lowered-to-sell-at-vetr-inc-updated-updated.html.Several large investors have recently made changes to their positions in the stock. Quantitative Systematic Strategies LLC purchased a new position in Abercrombie & Fitch during the second quarter worth approximately $250,000. Tower Research Capital LLC (trc) trimmed its stake by shedding 5,207 shares a decrease of 86.4%. Louisiana State Employees Retirement System now owns 27,700 shares of the apparel retailer's stock worth $345,000 after buying an additional 100 shares in the last quarter. Finally, New York State Teachers Retirement System boosted its stake in shares of Abercrombie & Fitch by 20.9% in the fourth quarter. Gotham Asset Management LLC now owns 519,181 shares of the apparel retailer's stock valued at $6,194,000 after buying an additional 307,728 shares in the last quarter. Credit Agricole S A bought a new stake in Abercrombie & Fitch during the fourth quarter worth approximately $120,000.Abercrombie & Fitch Co is a specialty retailer who primarily sells its products through store and direct-to-consumer operations, as well as through various wholesale, franchise and licensing arrangements. Tmall has carried the Hollister brand since 2014 and starting on July 26, it will also include a full offering of Abercrombie & Fitch and abercrombiekids products.


 




